Zhakupbaev, Deputy Chairperson, State Inspection, Ministry of
Agriculture , Astana , Kazakhstan

Summary
Report type Immediate notification
Start date 15/02/2012
Date of first confirmation of the event 17/02/2012
Report date 11/03/2012
Date submitted to OIE 11/03/2012
Reason for notification New strain of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease Clinical disease
Causal agent Foot and mouth disease virus
Serotype A
Nature of diagnosis Clinical, Laboratory (basic), Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

