Future Reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

[The previous outbreak in December of last year, 2011 was quite extensive and caused by serotype O. This report indicates two affected locations caused by serotype A - one of the serotypes in addition to O and Asia 1 selected for the vaccination campaign to stop the spread of the disease. Let's hope it can contain the spread this time.

Location of Dzahmbul in Kazakhstan on ProMEDmail/Healthmap is
available at: : http://healthmap.org/r/1_e4 . Mod FE]
